column2: SELECT TOP # g.objid, g.type, g.ra, g.dec, g.u, g.g, g.r, g.i, g.z, g.err_u, g.err_g, g.err_r, g.err_i, g.err_z, n.distance AS offset, pz.z AS redshift, pz.zErr AS err_redshift FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n JOIN Galaxy g ON n.objID=g.objID LEFT JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.objID=g.objID ORDER BY offset
